{"tid":1706954,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"(回帶)【陳雲又講大話】16年︰城邦歌是預備國歌；19年︰不是預備做國歌","createTime":"2019-11-11T08:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T08:20:51.000Z","uid":201464,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f1bfc4c3118bd668ed931b0a644a16a1aee254cd","tid":1706954,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:02:14.000Z","msg":"Credit：<br />\n<a href=\"https://newweb.hkgolden.com/thread/7116229/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewweb.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7116229%2Fpage%2F1&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddVe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=0c83007b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newweb.hkgolden.com/thread/7116229/page/1</a><br />\n眾所周知<br />\n呢期《願榮光歸香港》首歌一出就大熱唱到街知巷聞<br />\n仲講到國歌咁款<br />\n首歌掂唔掂我唔講啦但肯定既係好多人鍾意<br />\n而一向自以為懷才不遇既陳雲<br />\n當然就酸到出汁變左「酸根」<br />\n佢同成班青城派弟子瘋狂狙擊呢首歌<br />\n而點解陳雲唔乘機宣傳自己首《香港城邦歌》呢？<br />\n答案好簡單<br />\n因為首歌完全比唔上人地<br />\n除左d 詞係離晒地咁懶文雅<br />\n同埋有亞視風格應該長存不死之外<br />\n冇一樣野好過人地首歌<br />\n咁陳雲都識獻醜不如藏拙<br />\n所以齋抵毁而唔敢捧自己既歌<br />\n<br />\n而陳雲為左懶係冇私心咁呢<br />\n甚至連大話都講埋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10157406854632225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwan.chin.75%2Fposts%2F10157406854632225&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddVe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=75461ba4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10157406854632225</a><br />\n陳雲︰<br />\n我做事一向秉承正名之大義，《香港城邦歌》是香港城邦自治行動的戰歌，不是《香港之歌》，不是預備做香港國歌的，它只是自治的支持者偶然用來激勵士氣的。它只是城邦天使作的《城邦會戰勝歸來》的文雅版而已。<br />\n<br />\n但其實佢早係 2016 年果陣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10154286978327225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwan.chin.75%2Fposts%2F10154286978327225&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddVe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=d06ed012\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10154286978327225</a><br />\n陳雲︰<br />\n我的城邦自治及香港建國，倒是草擬好修訂《基本法》成為香港國的預備憲法，有復興會徽號的預備國旗，有《香港城邦歌》的預備國歌，也準備好遊說美國。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陳雲又再一次講大話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且當年d 青城信徒一早就吹奏首歌係國歌<br />\n例如︰<br />\n用《香港城邦歌》黎做香港國歌點睇！？<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6546898&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6546898%26page%3D1&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddVe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=79a5f7ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6546898&amp;page=1</a><br />\n香江19︰<br />\n城邦建國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係情何以堪？<br />\n完全證明左陳雲及其青城派<br />\n齋屌唔識做<br />\n做又做得柒<br />\n柒左又唔認<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而到青城派D 人當然不斷咁繼續狙擊《願榮光》啦<br />\n例如︰<br />\n曾鈺成讚《願榮光歸香港》高質 反映文宣水平相當高<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=7116165&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DCA%26message%3D7116165%26page%3D1&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddVe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=c199299d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=7116165&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\n咩敵人讚你<br />\n就證明你做錯左<br />\n但青城派弟子有冇諗過<br />\n其實陳雲係讚曾鈺成？<br />\n咁陳雲讚曾鈺成，曾鈺成讚首歌，咁陳雲&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/391914147490052\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwan.chin.75%2Fposts%2F391914147490052&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddVe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=50d174c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/391914147490052</a><br />\n陳雲︰<br />\n新近臨危受命的曾鈺成，是個對自己和對國家真誠的人，這是我對他的觀感。真正愛中國的人，也必定會支持一國兩制和愛護香港、珍惜香港，不會放任大陸人亂來。與他有數面之緣，他是個謙厚而沒機心的人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實點解陳雲首城邦歌會咁劣呢<br />\n出左咁多年<br />\n唔入屋、冇人識、冇人當係一回事？(青城弟子除外)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PErttjfrv1I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPErttjfrv1I&d=30k2sE%2FAiGmcVOPaBnjddVe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=e0d30f8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PErttjfrv1I</a><br />\n好簡單<br />\n佢係典型先作詞後作曲既作品<br />\n國語 / 普通話得四聲還好<br />\n但廣東話有九聲<br />\n一般黎講係要先作曲後作詞<br />\n咁先易入口易唱易記<br />\n不過當然啦<br />\n陳雲自詡老師<br />\n點會肯俾人先作一個好既曲<br />\n然後屈就填詞入去？<br />\n<br />\n佢自己懶係叻咁寫左一堆冇人識既字<br />\n然後叫D 後輩幫佢譜曲<br />\n結果就出左一首亞視劇集主題曲咁款<br />\n<br />\n而家知醜<br />\n唔敢再拎出黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2821b0367ddf92af9b08b6eb78ffe4f8bfef22f","tid":1706954,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:03:02.000Z","msg":"陳雲:香港戰局分析<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1706779/page/3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1706779/page/3</a><br />\n請負評及拉此post"},{"pid":"eabaa244578944c12d9576e7f69fb1c9718ce87d","tid":1706954,"uid":119895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:03:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e8b356fa3045b060702c40f1c79aa037e0350be0","tid":1706954,"uid":119895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UnopFA9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUnopFA9.jpg&h=66284eb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8e6b844997709ae03d4a52661b7f6f91ff9b918","tid":1706954,"uid":256783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:05:26.000Z","msg":"咪撚再講陳雲條垃圾啦"},{"pid":"be4a429f2a523eac48bd6ae79cc3dd780bde0d4c","tid":1706954,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:06:13.000Z","msg":"見陳雲即拉"},{"pid":"3a8ce7d9ddb513716474f1090ea23decd86ec029","tid":1706954,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:06:50.000Z","msg":"今日唔好推陳雲條撚樣好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a82818e11c3808f2aca99befe585d3a0c0b5e1","tid":1706954,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:07:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陳雲:香港戰局分析<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1706779/page/3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1706779/page/3</a><br />\n請負評及拉此post</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1ab2d95cac0bece13e6f2d32766cfe30714b0e88","tid":1706954,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:20:51.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"}]}